Client rewrite
body:
This PR is a Work in Progress for a client rewrite.

Goal of this PR is to have stable, performant, well tested Core NATS capabilities with most features in.

This PR does not and will not contain JetStream, KV, ObjectStore. 
Those will be added after this is merged.

This PR also changes the structure of the repo to support both old and new client, at least until new Client has feature parity with sync client.

- [x] Publish
- [x] Subscribe
- [ ] Unsubscribe (@caspervonb)
- [x] Make `Client` clonable
- [ ] Reconnections (@caspervonb)
- [x] TLS
- [x] client initiated flushes
- [ ] no responders
- [ ] lame duck mode
- [ ] async error callbacks/handling
- [x] test coverage
- [ ] bencharks
- [x] add flush once in a while
